<ul class="simple">
<li>Fixed a potential security issue in build 20100805 where in certain
circumstances guest users might be incorrectly recognized as an
authentic member.</li>
<li>Fixed a bug (#13516) where the language translation utility failed
due to new language file naming scheme created in the last build.</li>
